title: Useful book for russian learners
description:
The book is in origin german: Atlas of philosophy dtv (Kunzman)





The point is: as long as throughout the book you find a double page , 

              one of text and one of graphic explication , 

              you can print 10 , 20 , 30 pages and put them together with the

              physical book in your own language (french , spanish etc) and 

              compare the texts. This is possible , 

              due to the fact that this book is present in almost all public

              libraries across Europe.
